data.meta_description: ISSN INTERNATIONAL STANDARD SERIAL NUMBER is a trademark of CIEPS-ISSN. Filed in April 22 (2015), the ISSN INTERNATIONAL STANDARD SERIAL NUMBER covers Compilation of data into computer databases in the field of business directories and advertising; systematization of information in computer databases
